entry.title: Release Notes
entry.content:
Data updates up to September 2018.

The following changes have been delivered in this release:

  1. Update: Data download files updated up to September 2018 (when applicable).
  2. Update: The Performance Review Commission (PRC) quarterly online review is now online.
  3. Update: Vertical flight efficiency workshop on Monday, 26 November 2018.
    Due to the high interest, the workshop was moved to a larger meeting room.
    If you are interested, please register here before the 5 November 2018.

Release Notes was originally published by European Organisation for the Safety of Air Navigation (EUROCONTROL) on PRU

entry.title: Release Notes
entry.content:
Data updates up to August 2018.

The following changes have been delivered in this release:

  1. Update: Data download files updated up to July 2018 (when applicable).
  2. New: A specific analysis of en route delays attributed to ATC capacity and staffing is now available.
  3. New: A specific analysis of en route delays attributed to weather is now available.
  4. New: A specific analysis of en route delays attributed to ATC disruptions (strike, equipment) is now available.

Release Notes was originally published by European Organisation for the Safety of Air Navigation (EUROCONTROL) on PRU

entry.title: Release Notes
entry.content:
Data updates up to Dec 2017.

The following changes have been delivered in this release:

  1. Update: Data download files updated up to Dec 2017 (when applicable).
  2. NEW: The interactive ACE online dashboard is now available online.
    The new interactive online dashboard enables interested stakeholders to access the latest available ACE data and analysis. Using the interactive functionalities of the dashboard, stakeholders can design and customise specific analyses and presentations covering the 2002-2015 period.

Release Notes was originally published by European Organisation for the Safety of Air Navigation (EUROCONTROL) on PRU
